    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "On 31 July 47, [REDACTED] of the Idaho Daily Statesman, tele-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "phoned Lt. Brown requesting he return to Tacoma because [REDACTED] believed he had some",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "very vital information on the flying disc.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "Lt. Brown and Capt. Davidson interviewed a [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "[REDACTED] along with [REDACTED] of the United Air Lines, and [REDACTED] at the Win-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "throp Hotel in Tacoma, Washington, on the night of 31 July 1947.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "The summary of their interrogation and findings was related to Major Sander,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "Public Information Officer, McChord Field, by [REDACTED] Smith. Major",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Sander retold the results of the investigation to this officer from his notes.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "[REDACTED] were not available for interview while this officer",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "was in that area, although every effort was made to contact them.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "Further investigation of this particular incident was left with Mr. Brody,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "Resident Agent, FBI, Tacoma, Washington.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "It was apparent from newspaper clippings, telephone calls to this officer, and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "conversations with Major Sander, that a United Press correspondent, of the Tacoma",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "Times, was instrumental in keeping this case alive. This officer and Major Sander,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "although quoted many times in the press, did not discuss this matter with the press",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "during the period of this report.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
